<h2 class="sectionedit1" id="dnkk_kano_flight_information_region">DNKK Kano Flight Information Region</h2>
<div class="level2">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> The Kano FIR covers the entirety of Nigeria&#039;s borders. It is neighbored by Accra FIR in the West, the Niamey FIR in the North, the N&#039;Djamena FIR, the Northeast and Brazzaville in the East and Accra Oceanic in the South.</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
