<div id="dwpl-ti-content" class="dwpl-ti-content"><div class="dwpl-ti-tab-embd hidden"><div class="dwpl-ti-permalink-header"><a href="/dnkk-rules" >>> Go to this page.</a></div>

<h2 class="sectionedit1" id="dnkk_kano_airspace_rules">DNKK Kano Airspace Rules</h2>
<div class="level2">

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;DNKK Kano Airspace Rules&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;dnkk_kano_airspace_rules&quot;,&quot;codeblockOffset&quot;:0,&quot;secid&quot;:1,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;1-38&quot;} -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2" id="separation">Separation</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Satellite based ADS-B coverage is available in the Kano sector and as such, the following separation standards are to be applied:</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>

<h4 id="vertical_separation">Vertical Separation</h4>
<div class="level4">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Separation of 1000 ft in RVSM airspace and below then 2000 ft above RVSM airspace</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>

<h4 id="horizontal_separation">Horizontal Separation</h4>
<div class="level4">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Separation of 5 NM between position symbols but may be increased to 10 NM if required.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Separation of 5 NM between position symbol between an aircraft in Climb or Descent configuration and another stable aircraft at a flight level provided that the climbing or descending aircraft crosses the level of stable traffic only behind said traffic. </div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Separation&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;separation&quot;,&quot;codeblockOffset&quot;:0,&quot;secid&quot;:2,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;39-695&quot;} -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3" id="selcal">SELCAL</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> DNKK Kano does NOT offer SELCAL capabilities.</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SELCAL&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;selcal&quot;,&quot;codeblockOffset&quot;:0,&quot;secid&quot;:3,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;696-764&quot;} -->
<h3 class="sectionedit4" id="slop">SLOP</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> The use of SLOP at DNKK Kano is in compliance with provisions in ICAO Doc. 4444, between flight level FL290 and FL410 on all enroute ATS routes.</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SLOP&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;slop&quot;,&quot;codeblockOffset&quot;:0,&quot;secid&quot;:4,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;765-930&quot;} -->
<h3 class="sectionedit5" id="vfr_rules">VFR Rules</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Flights over populous areas are not allowed below 1500 ft above the highest obstacle within a radius of 2000 ft from the aircraft.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> </div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;plugin_include_start&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;dn-footer&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;secid&quot;:6,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;0-&quot;} --><div class="plugin_include_content plugin_include__dn-footer">
<div class="level3">
<hr />

<p>
<a href="/dnkk" class="wikilink1" title="dnkk" data-wiki-id="dnkk">DNKK</a> Kano FIR | v0.1
</p>

</div>
