<h2 class="sectionedit1" id="dnkk_kano_free_route_airspace">DNKK Kano Free Route Airspace</h2>
<div class="level2">

</div>
<!-- EDIT{&quot;target&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;DNKK Kano Free Route Airspace&quot;,&quot;hid&quot;:&quot;dnkk_kano_free_route_airspace&quot;,&quot;codeblockOffset&quot;:0,&quot;secid&quot;:1,&quot;range&quot;:&quot;1-43&quot;} -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2" id="fra_waypoints">FRA Waypoints</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Controllers may redirect any flights from/to a FRA Entry/Exit Waypoint to a FRA Arrival/Departure Connecting Waypoint or from a FRA Entry Waypoint to a FRA Exit Waypoint.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Controllers may never redirect any flight that may cross Restricted or Special User Airspace. In those circumstances, controllers may use the FRA Intermediate Waypoints to redirect the flights.</div>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="table sectionedit3"><table class="inline">
	<thead>
	<tr class="row0">
		<th class="col0 leftalign"> Waypoint  </th><th class="col1 leftalign"> Type  </th><th class="col2"> Flight Levels </th><th class="col3 leftalign"> Level Availablty  </th><th class="col4"> Remarks </th>
	</tr>
	</thead>
	<tr class="row1">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> KELAK     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row2">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> GATAG     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row3">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> NANOS     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row4">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> KORUT     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row5">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> ARDEX     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row6">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> MIMBA     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row7">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> OBUDU     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EXAD  </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row8">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> POLTO     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> EX    </td><td class="col2 leftalign"> ODD / EVEN    </td><td class="col3 leftalign"> FL245 / UNLTD     </td><td class="col4"> - </td>
